attributionInfo.brokerName: Campion & Company Fine Homes Real Estate

description: Stunning 2 bed, 2 bath, duplex penthouse with unobstructed city views in prime Southie location! Kitchen features s/s appliances, quartz counters, and a large island that is perfect for entertaining. First floor includes your open concept living/dining room, laundry and the first of 2 bathrooms. The spacious king-sized bedroom, with double closets, is loaded with light. Large guest room is a functional space, currently used as a home office/gym. The SPACIOUS PRIVATE PATIO is a true gem - perfect for outdoor dining. Additional features include 10 ft ceilings, NEST Thermostat, and custom window treatments. TWO DEEDED GARAGE PARKING SPACES, oversized private storage, professionally managed, bike room and elevator. Easy commuter access to Broadway Red Line, bus and minutes to Logan, I-93/I-90.
